reqBody.prompt: A mage, a guardian of light, she has short brown hair. She wears a glowing colour palette of white, gold, deep blue, and dress boots. She is standing with her arms outstretched to the sides, palms facing downwards, and her legs slightly apart with a slight bend in her knees. Reference sheet. Chroma key background. Her hands and legs are equally outstretched to the sides, her palms facing downwards, and her knees barefoot apart. The background is deep black. She is straight on, facing the viewer.
